On Fri, 9 May 2025 at 12:23 pm, Cindy Valderama <cindy@wolfiq.com.au> wrote:
Hi Brendan.

We've reviewed the setup for the booking appointments and noticed that there's currently no automation in place. At the moment, our team manually updates the available team members on the site based on internal scheduling.

To improve this process, we propose creating a custom classification linked to the Team Members post type. This would include:
  • Physiotherapy
    • Next Therapist Available
    • Select Therapist
  • Exercise Physiology
With this classification in place, you'll be able to easily assign team members to categories like "Next Therapist Available" and "Select Therapist."

On the front end, we can dynamically display the appropriate therapist names along with their availability based on the classification-making the experience smoother for users and easier to manage on your end.

We estimate this implementation will take around 5 hours.

Would you like us to go ahead with this enhancement?
